headline: French swimmer Maxime Grousset clinches third world title in butterfly
description: After taking gold in the 50m butterfly on Monday, Grousset once again became a world champion in the 100m butterfly in Singapore on Saturday. This double victory, along with new French and European records, has confirmed his talent in a stroke that was never his main focus.
